name: DoMyjeans
tag_list: jeans, denim, custom, tailor-made, plus-size, perfect-jeans, slim, straight, bootcut
overview:
You always imagined the jeans of your dreams. DMJ proposes you to make in less than 10 minutes a unique pair of jeans deliverable within 21 days.

Enter the world of DMJ and express your creativity, your desires, and your choices. Whether you like denim or wish to be at the top of fashion, you are right now just a few clicks away from your self-created and customized jeans. No more constraints of styles, colors, dimensions, sizes, everything is possible.

For less than $135USD, you can customize jeans tailored with excellent manufacturing quality, design jeans to fit your style, or offer personalized and original presents.
